Package: thesisTreeTraversal
Type: Package
Title: Phylogenetic Tree Traversal Benchmark Wrapper for Thesis Comparison
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Thesis", "Author", email = "thesis@example.invalid",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Thin wrapper around ape::read.tree() and ape::postorder()
    exposing a single callable function that parses a Newick string and
    runs a postorder traversal accumulating basic tree statistics.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    ape (>= 5.8-1)
Suggests:
    bench (>= 1.1.4)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
